Prerequisites
==============
python
virtualenv, which you can install with "sudo easy_install virtualenv"

How to install
==============
git clone https://jawspeak@github.com/jawspeak/tw-california-tshirt-generator.git

cd tw-california-tshirt-generator
virtualenv tw_tshirt_env   #this creates a new virtualenv
. tw_tshirt_env/bin/activate
./bootstrap.py  #this installs everything into your virtualenv
# optionally, edit the constants in the script, or change the filenames to blahblah=A clever caption.jpg
python ./design_shirts_from_california.py
look at the tshirt-sumbissions-made-in-california.pdf


******* Inspired from my Awesome TWU award printer https://github.com/jawspeak/twu-pdf-award-printers ********
